22:26.680 --> 22:29.593
<i>It failed,
but Hank was seriously injured</i>

22:29.760 --> 22:32.036
<i>and I wound up
paying his medical bills,</i>

22:32.240 --> 22:36.314
<i>which amounted
to a little over $177,000.</i>

22:36.480 --> 22:40.713
<i>Upon recovery,
Hank was bent on revenge.</i>

22:41.560 --> 22:45.793
<i>Working with a man
named Hector Salamanca,</i>

22:45.960 --> 22:47.872
<i>he plotted to kill Fring.</i>

