22:56.520 --> 22:59.877
<i>I have often contemplated suicide,</i>

23:00.040 --> 23:02.271
<i>but I'm a coward.</i>

23:04.680 --> 23:07.070
<i>I wanted to go to the police...</i>

23:08.600 --> 23:10.239
<i>but I was frightened.</i>

23:10.680 --> 23:15.197
<i>Hank had risen to become the head
of the Albuquerque DEA.</i>

23:15.360 --> 23:18.592
<i>To keep me in line,
