23:42.520 --> 23:45.911
<i>Recently, I tried once again to quit,</i>

23:46.080 --> 23:50.154
<i>and in response, he gave me this.</i>

23:59.640 --> 24:01.871
<i>I can't take this anymore.</i>

24:03.360 --> 24:07.240
<i>I live in fear every day
