28:00.120 --> 28:02.794
I mean, he knows you're Heisenberg.

28:02.960 --> 28:04.952
But I figure not much else,

28:05.160 --> 28:07.277
otherwise, you know,
you'd be locked up.

28:09.840 --> 28:12.150
What did he say exactly?

28:13.160 --> 28:16.471
He wants me
to inform on you for him.

28:16.640 --> 28:18.632
Tell him everything we did.

28:20.840 --> 28:21.990
Anything else?

28:24.040 --> 28:27.636
I don't think he's told
the rest of the DEA.

28:28.440 --> 28:30.079
Why do you say that?

28:30.240 --> 28:32.994
Just him being there all by himself

28:33.160 --> 28:36.756
and, plus,
he was acting kind of shady.

28:36.920 --> 28:39.435
Seemed like
he didn't want the other cops

28:39.600 --> 28:42.274
hearing what he had to say.
Mm.

28:42.440 --> 28:46.275
Are we gonna talk about the rain of caca
the kid brought down upon us?

28:46.440 --> 28:49.274
Want to hazard a guess
what his little charity drive cost you?

28:49.440 --> 28:51.511
Why don't you go
take a walk, Saul?

29:01.520 --> 29:04.354
Jesse, will you let me help you?

29:05.480 --> 29:08.393
I don't like to see you
hurting like this.

29:11.360 --> 29:13.636
Maybe it's time for a change.

29:16.440 --> 29:17.999
What kind of change?

29:19.600 --> 29:21.273
I don't know.

29:25.240 --> 29:27.675
I don't know, maybe...

29:28.960 --> 29:31.634
Maybe it's time
for you to just

29:32.320 --> 29:34.960
leave all of this behind.

29:36.160 --> 29:37.879
Just get out of town.

29:38.040 --> 29:39.838
Don't look back.

29:45.880 --> 29:47.951
Saul knows a man.

29:49.760 --> 29:54.357
He specializes in giving people
new identities.

29:55.600 --> 29:59.150
He would move you
someplace far away

29:59.320 --> 30:02.154
and set you up
with a whole new life.

30:03.720 --> 30:08.272
Yeah, I know,
sounds a little extreme.

30:11.520 --> 30:14.592
But maybe it's exactly
what you need.

30:16.040 --> 30:18.839
You know, I really think
that would be good for you.

30:19.040 --> 30:20.759
A clean slate.

30:22.120 --> 30:24.589
All right, just think about it.

30:24.800 --> 30:29.272
You get a job, something
legitimate, something you like.

30:30.520 --> 30:32.796
Meet a girl,
start a family, even.

30:32.960 --> 30:36.317
Hell, you're still
so damn young. Heh.

30:37.480 --> 30:40.314
