ahead of you

30:50.320 --> 30:53.233
with a chance to hit
the reset button.

30:54.680 --> 30:56.717
In a few years,

30:57.680 --> 31:01.993
this might all feel like
nothing more than a bad dream.

31:14.720 --> 31:16.951
Would you just, for once,

31:17.120 --> 31:19.396
