31:32.600 --> 31:35.991
Yes. Yes, you are.

31:36.200 --> 31:39.079
All right, just drop the whole
concerned-dad thing

31:39.240 --> 31:41.471
and tell me the truth.

31:41.640 --> 31:44.075
I mean, you're acting like

31:44.240 --> 31:46.709
