32:01.160 --> 32:03.720
Just ask me for a favor.

32:05.080 --> 32:07.470
Just tell me you don't
give a shit about me

32:07.640 --> 32:09.393
and it's either this...

32:10.600 --> 32:15.550
It's either this or you'll kill me
the same way you killed Mike.

32:16.800 --> 32:19.759
