what this is all about?

32:20.920 --> 32:24.231
Us meeting
way the hell out here.

32:25.960 --> 32:28.520
In case I say no.

32:31.760 --> 32:33.513
Come on.

32:34.800 --> 32:37.634
Just tell me you need this.

33:34.760 --> 33:36.194
Your change.

33:36.360 --> 33:38.716
If you'll hand this
to your car wash professional

33:38.880 --> 33:40.951
and have an A-1 day.

