the register for me?

34:03.080 --> 34:04.673
Skyler?

34:12.480 --> 34:14.277
It worked

34:15.040 --> 34:17.190
and we're fine.

34:18.920 --> 34:20.717
Okay?

34:22.760 --> 34:24.478
We're fine.

34:59.720 --> 35:01.074
So Palmer and Castanares

35:01.280 --> 35:03.749
are sitting on that jerkoff
Saul Goodman's office,

35:03.920 --> 35:06.754
keeping an eye on Jesse Pinkman.
Yeah, I put them on it.

35:06.920 --> 35:08.832
You wanna explain that
to me?

35:09.800 --> 35:12.156
Yeah. Right.

35:12.320 --> 35:15.996
Why the hell should I know anything?
They're just my guys, after all.

35:16.680 --> 35:18.459
You gotta tell me what's going on.

35:18.559 --> 35:20.594
Pinkman is A.P.D.'s problem, not ours.

35:20.800 --> 35:22.314
You got a history with this kid.

35:22.480 --> 35:24.597
