36:00.400 --> 36:02.153
You have that 3:00.

36:02.320 --> 36:03.993
Will you be back?

36:04.160 --> 36:07.710
You know what, it's gonna have
to be another day. Reschedule it.

36:11.080 --> 36:12.205
Last chance.

36:12.305 --> 36:14.073
You sure there's nobody
you wanna say bye to?

36:14.240 --> 36:16.038
Nobody at all?

36:16.200 --> 36:17.714
No.

36:17.880 --> 36:21.635
This is it. Once I make the call,
there's no take-backs.

36:28.400 --> 36:29.800
Uh, I need a new dust filter

36:30.000 --> 36:33.391
for my Hoover Max Extract
Pressure Pro, model 60.

36:33.560 --> 36:35.791
Can you help me with that?

36:36.000 --> 36:37.150
