36:41.600 --> 36:45.514
Currently out on bail.
Yeah, he knows the rules.

36:46.000 --> 36:48.834
One hour.
Okay, he'll be there.

36:51.200 --> 36:52.839
And done.

36:56.280 --> 36:57.600
Okay,

36:57.760 --> 37:00.195
