37:00.400 --> 37:02.517
Your benefactor

37:02.680 --> 37:05.320
asked me to send you out
with something extra.

37:05.480 --> 37:06.914
Get you started, you know?

37:07.120 --> 37:08.873
Keep you sitting pretty

37:09.080 --> 37:11.879
until you get into the groove
of your new life.

37:12.080 --> 37:16.040
Provided, of course, you don't
toss it out the window on the way.

37:17.040 --> 37:20.112
Seriously, this is the last of it

37:20.280 --> 37:23.159
so you might wanna think
about making a budget.

37:23.320 --> 37:24.720
Hey, whoa, whoa,
what are you doing?

37:24.880 --> 37:27.679
