41:57.160 --> 41:58.150
Why didn't you...?

42:00.040 --> 42:01.315
Stop! Unh!

42:02.440 --> 42:03.590
Code red!

42:06.680 --> 42:08.956
Huell!
No! Hey!

42:09.120 --> 42:10.395
