43:46.920 --> 43:49.799
Oh, I... I did. I'm... I'm so sorry.

43:49.960 --> 43:53.032
Um, here you go.

43:53.200 --> 43:54.759
Thank you for your honesty.

43:54.920 --> 43:58.152
