Nope. Things are fine.

44:19.920 --> 44:21.832
Good.
Why?

44:22.000 --> 44:24.834
Oh, no reason.

44:32.880 --> 44:36.271
You know what I found the other day

44:36.480 --> 44:41.430
is that the... The... The latch
on the soda machine wasn't...

44:43.440 --> 44:45.193
latching.

44:45.360 --> 44:49.559
It's... It's catching every time
